<DOCNO> NYT20000321.0049 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-03-21 04:25 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3318 &Cx1f; tab-z
r k BC-PUTIN-MYSTERY-MAN-RES     03-21 1222
