<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Timely tips for tax season
 &HT;    By Hank Ezell
 &HT;    c. 2000 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   ATLANTA _ Three out of four American taxpayers expect to get
refunds from the Internal Revenue Service this year.
</P>
