   LIVABILITY AT DC RANCH: THEY'VE GOT IT WIRED
</P>
<P>
   Every house at the DC Ranch planned community north of Phoenix
has two 256K Internet connections that are always available without
dialing an access number. Every household can have up to six e-mail
