<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-03-21 15:33 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3624 &Cx1f; taf-z
u i BC-INDIA-KASHMIR-NYT &LR;      03-21 0912
