u f BC-HOTEL-SUIT22-COX     03-21 0635
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-HOTEL-SUIT22-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    ADAM'S MARK HOTEL CHAIN SETTLES TWO DISCRIMINATION LAWSUITS
