   POPE-HOLYLAND (Jerusalem) _ Saying he felt deep emotion setting
foot in Israel, ``the land where God chose to pitch his tent,''
Pope John Paul arrived in Tel Aviv on Tuesday, and was instantly
given a taste of the kind of fierce political intensity that will
