<HEADLINE>
 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by N.Y. Times News Service clients)  
 
The Arizona Republic plans to move the following stories for use by
clients of the NYTimes News Service for Wednesday, March 22. If you
have any questions, please call The Republic News Desk at (602)
444-8286.
<TEXT>
<P>
   &QL; 
 &QL; 
DOMESTIC (Phoenix) - San Diego Padres outfielder Al Martin and a
woman who claims to be his wife are both arrested on domestic
violence charges after a fight over Martin's alleged bigamy. It's
the latest in a string of domestic violence cases involving
professional athletes. By DENNIS WAGNER. Story will move in the `A`
category. &QL; 
