   DESGRIPPES-AD-COLUMN (New York) _ A low-profile international
design and image firm, Desgrippes Gobe &AMP; Associates, which has
high-profile clients like Air France, Coca-Cola and The Limited, is
creating a new identity for a client it has known forever: itself.
By Jane L. Levere.
