Spotted dick (aka spotted dog) pudding from the Pudding Club at
Three Ways House in Mickleton - started in 1985 by a bunch of
die-hard chauvinists determined to beat back the assault of frozen
supermarket Black Forest gateaux. (Jonathan Player/The New York
